---
title: Buffalo Chicken Lettuce Wraps with Tangy Blue Cheese Coleslaw
description: Leave it to the HF chefs to come up with the perfect filling for fresh, crisp baby lettuce leaves: Tender sautéed chicken and shredded carrots tossed with tangy-spicy Buffalo sauce. Load it all into lettuce leaves, top with creamy blue cheese coleslaw and a squeeze of fresh lemon juice, and prepare to be wowed!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/668c361b9a3c9af871e5f9af-6ee32453.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/668c361b9a3c9af871e5f9af-en-US.pdf
time required: 20 minutes
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 500 kcal
  fat: 28 g
  saturated fat: 10 g
  carbohydrates: 21 g
  sugar: 10 g
